thread.title: Tourists snap up royal wedding memorabillia

title: Tourists snap up royal wedding memorabillia
text:
Tourists snap up royal wedding memorabillia 12:14pm EDT - 01:46
Whether you love them or hate them, anyone visiting the British town of Windsor can't escape Prince Harry and Meghan Markle's faces which are emblazoned on merchandise in shops across the picturesque town. As Kate King reports, some estimates suggest the wedding could give the economy a £500 million boost.
